verses.verse: Behold <S%H1288><s%>, bless you the Lord <S%H3068><s%>, all you servants <S%H5650><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%>, which by night <S%H3915><s%> stand <S%H5975><s%> in the house <S%H1004><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%>.
Lift up <S%H5375><s%> your hands <S%H3027><s%> in the sanctuary <S%H6944><s%>, and bless <S%H1288><s%> the Lord <S%H3068><s%>.
The Lord <S%H3068><s%> that made <S%H6213><s%> heaven <S%H8064><s%> and earth <S%H776><s%> bless <S%H1288><s%> you out of Zion <S%H6726><s%>.
